.description
A powerful ISO/ANSI text reader which strictly follows Commodore's
application guidelines.  Features include unlimited number of windows on
any public screen, scrolling with both mouse and keys, full AUISG menus and
ARexx commands, clipboard support, AppWindows, fast and residentable
activator, full configurability of the keyboard, preferences file and
editor to change preferences, background mode, and more.  
